title: Super Bowl LII Recap, Foles And Pederson Take Down Brady And Belichick (Football 02/05)
description:
Nick Kostos, Will Brinson, and Pete Prisco recap all angles of Super Bowl LII and the Eagles victory over the Patriots. The guys discuss Doug Pederson's gutsy playcalling, Nick Foles confident and impressive performance, Malcolm Butler missing, Belichick, Brady and much more!
